Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only hold that shadow technique for about five minutes before you run out of juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now we're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This's the best possible situation for me, you dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including my own, I had five hearts total.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi, it's only fitting that I take yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to replace the one you destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sent them out separately, and now they're joined?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The masks that merged were the fire and wind ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi, I'm going to rip out your heart to replace the one you destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to force me into an open area and shoot me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your idea of hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did an excellent job of concealing yourself this time, Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have the courage to stand before me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suiton, Suijinheki{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.95,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Suiton, Suijinheki: Water Element, Circular Water Wall)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water attacks aren't enough to stop a fire-wind combination?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only option is to fight him at close-range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you couldn't manage to account for my attacks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'll take your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain is glorious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jashin must be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kakuzu should be about done by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not deep enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little prick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the fuck are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little prick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the fuck are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just playing possum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood on your spike isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your partner's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used {\i1}your{\i0} blood for your partner's ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kakashi-sensei, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use it when you see an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru knew that blood was the key to his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he prepared several special blood capsules before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did you-?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't matter who, we just needed a \Nchance to get some of Kakuzu's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this capsule, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you even have the chance...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I punched a hole in your chest with my Raikiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that same moment, I filled a capsule with your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll capture him by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll fulfill {\i0}that{\i1} role as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I took that, it became my job to corner you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where the hell are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trying to separate me from Kakuzu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure you want to let him go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's severely underestimating Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Shikamaru kid would've become a big bounty one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now, he'll be dead by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was our plan all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sons a bitches...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that kid...to have planned so far ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have planned more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two severely underestimated Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He refused to let the knowledge that Asuma died for go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men like you who kill without hesitation could never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They invaded his body so far in such a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shikamaru had taken a second longer, he'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull them out slowly, so you don't damage the blood vessels!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal you with medical techniques right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Baika no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chou Harite{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.35,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Chou Harite: Mega Palm Thrust)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Good one, Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He absorbed the lightning creature's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even his main body is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've destroyed two of my hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ages since anyone's managed that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a thickhead like me knows what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been like a thousand times at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, any dumbass could figure out your technique after seeing it so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadow ain't as strong as it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes is your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you bind someone with your technique, \Nthe effect lessens as time passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the longer you use it, the weaker it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost outta chakra, ain'tcha? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatake Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to replace the hearts I've lost with yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stock up on hearts anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fuuton, Rasengan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.85,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Fuuton, Rasengan: Wind Element, Spiraling Sphere)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suiton, Hahonryuu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.02,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Suiton, Hahonryuu: Water Element, Crashing Rapids)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gufuu Suika no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.24,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Gufuu Suika no Jutsu: Water Typhoon Vortex Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His snoring's so loud that I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H2D2D2D&\4c&H2D2D2D&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H2D2D2D&\4c&H2D2D2D&}Wait up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a rough sleeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to sleep like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Naruto! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he slept through all that ruckus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-senpai, that's just not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatake Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to replace the hearts I've lost with yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stock up on hearts anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fuuton, Rasengan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suiton, Hahonryuu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gufuu Suika no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backup... We're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura! Sai-san! And Naruto, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you so beat up, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy must be extremely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see we've got another comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already look worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting this guy's partner somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of you go back Shikamaru up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One long-range fighter and one medical ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Sai, Sakura, follow Pakkun and help Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:23:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:23:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think your reinforcements will do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have a wider variety of new hearts to choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.28,0:24:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.66,0:24:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he finish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.15,0:24:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's about halfway there, if that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.88,0:24:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.94,0:24:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to see a completely new Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.51,0:25:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the situation was, he shouldn't have gone up against the person who killed Asuma-san by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Shikamaru-kun's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.15,0:25:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.31,0:25:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.68,0:25:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the smartest person in the Fire Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.42,0:25:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.79,0:25:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess we should head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.83,0:25:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, he isn't the least bit motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's actually a squad captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.08,0:25:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.88,0:25:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just not good at showing his enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:25:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, he hates showing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.92,0:26:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll complain about how annoying it is while working up a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.27,0:26:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.75,0:26:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunade-sama, are you sure you aren't overestimating Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.21,0:26:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think I may still be underestimating him a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.77,0:26:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a formal request from the Fire Country's Feudal Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.59,0:26:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says that he'd like to have Shikamaru join his personal guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Shikamaru caught the Feudal Lord's eye. His people saw how efficiently he ran the last Chuunin exam and thought he'd be a great leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.05,0:26:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's the first step to becoming one of the 12 Guardian Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.30,0:26:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.83,0:26:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.80,0:26:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did Shikamaru accept the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.23,0:27:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.29,0:27:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you refused the Feudal Lord's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.12,0:27:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.59,0:27:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, going out and seeing the outside world isn't such a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.45,0:27:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man I am today because of my experience \Nwith the 12 Guardian Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.42,0:27:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.94,0:27:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna deal with any extra trouble in the future, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.76,0:27:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.89,0:27:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.03,0:28:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji, Ino, the guys in my current squad, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.21,0:28:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just staying in the village 'cause I'd be worried about them otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.81,0:28:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.26,0:28:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have the Will of Fire in you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.36,0:28:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Will of Fire... That's something the Third talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.69,0:28:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. It refers to the strong will that protects our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's nothing to write home about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.97,0:28:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to protect them because you care about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.49,0:28:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.27,0:28:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all Konoha shinobi. It's troublesome, but I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.77,0:28:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Will of Fire brings light to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.34,0:28:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least that's what my dad always said.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.25,0:29:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someday you'll illuminate the village to, Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.60,0:29:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.29,0:29:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry about Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.79,0:29:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting to avenge Asuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.69,0:29:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he made a foolproof plan before challenging the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.29,0:29:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.84,0:29:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.62,0:29:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.30,0:30:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had you devoted your life to Lord Jashin, he might've saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.05,0:30:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, even if you converted right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.39,0:30:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'd never forgive you, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.47,0:30:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your messed-up God's forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.74,0:30:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kageyose no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.74,0:30:34.62,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Kageyose no Jutsu: Shadow Summoning Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.53,0:30:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.98,0:30:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have enough chakra for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.28,0:31:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.58,0:31:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.95,0:31:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.33,0:31:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.24,0:31:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.92,0:31:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you set this up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.59,0:31:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had this all prepared before we came out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.75,0:31:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wasn't just trying to be the hero and separate me and Kakuzu. He led me out here on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.70,0:32:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means he planned this out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.11,0:32:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You dig two holes when you curse someone."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.19,0:32:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.09,0:32:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.89,0:32:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you kill someone with a curse, you'll be killed in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.76,0:32:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that the curse ends up burying two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.14,0:32:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your curse killed my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.53,0:32:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you thought you'd get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.13,0:32:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hole is your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.51,0:32:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.42,0:32:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you destroy my body, and I'm left with nothing but my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.71,0:32:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll escape somehow, and when I do, \NI'll find you and bite your fuckin' throat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.28,0:32:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.04,0:32:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.79,0:33:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This forest is a special part of the Fire Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.97,0:33:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only people from my clan are permitted to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.84,0:33:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else ever comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.41,0:33:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My clan will keep you trapped here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.80,0:33:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got him, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.41,0:33:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.23,0:34:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entrust my Will of Fire to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.33,0:34:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! What the hell were you lighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.26,0:34:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Will of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.89,0:34:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The powerful will that protects our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.35,0:34:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.32,0:35:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tajuu Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.63,0:35:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mass Shadow Clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.98,0:35:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're the Nine Tails Jinchuuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.73,0:35:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please brief us on the enemy's abilities and the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against two members of Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.13,0:35:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru is fighting one, as I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.91,0:35:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one is standing right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.19,0:35:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's able to split off parts of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.63,0:35:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of those masked creatures can be detached as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.20,0:35:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one of them has its own heart and is able to maneuver on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.31,0:35:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, he had five hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.76,0:36:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've destroyed two of them, so he's down to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.69,0:36:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.49,0:36:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we've killed him twice already,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.65,0:36:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we have to kill him three more times to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.13,0:36:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a mid-range fighter and can use high-level \Ntechniques of every element.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.63,0:36:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder senpai had his hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.15,0:36:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.07,0:36:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard him loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.10,0:36:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.17,0:36:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just attack him head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.95,0:36:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only used shadow clones?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.89,0:36:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nearly enough, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.43,0:36:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fighting style combined with his speed means I need at least three shadow clones to distract him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.39,0:36:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used the clones to get some experience fighting him, then gained their knowledge when they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.02,0:37:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's formulating a plan of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.98,0:37:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's learned how to use shadow clones on a whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.65,0:37:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tajuu Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.59,0:37:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three clones?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.80,0:37:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some screech...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.63,0:37:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And the chakra's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.26,0:37:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.67,0:38:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as I've gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.74,0:38:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll test it by smashing it into my Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.17,0:38:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.06,0:38:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what's supposed to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.59,0:38:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your technique's almost complete, then my Rasengan should be completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.33,0:38:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.95,0:39:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.36,0:39:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that technique?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.02,0:39:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get hit with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.57,0:39:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.23,0:39:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fuuton, Rasen-Shuriken{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.23,0:39:37.57,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Fuuton, Rasen-Shuriken: Wind Element, Spiraling Shuriken)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.71,0:41:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teamwork's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.09,0:41:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm standing at a dangerous bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.73,0:41:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to cross over that bridge by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.80,0:41:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't make it to the other side, I'll never grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.51,0:41:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't take that bridge away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.79,0:41:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wind Element, Rasen-Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.36,0:41:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.57,0:41:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.19,0:41:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is Team Eight's order to stay on standby gonna last?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.39,0:41:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.94,0:41:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Kurenai-sensei's heart has been terribly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.18,0:41:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.64,0:42:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Ten's taken off to go avenge Asuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.80,0:42:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like Naruto's working hard on developing some new technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.69,0:42:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto-kun's working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.43,0:42:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.17,0:42:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! It's nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.45,0:42:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.00,0:42:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm gonna drop by and see Kurenai-sensei on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.63,0:42:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Akamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.33,0:42:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiba-kun, wait up! Kiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.83,0:42:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.86,0:42:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sky is too vast for a person to live life alone.
